nodes.text: A Brief History of the Mandalorians

A Brief History of the Mandalorians is an article that appeared in Star Wars Insider 115 written by Leland Y. Chee. The article traced the appearances of the Mandalorians from its early concept all the way to the Legacy era.
Star Wars Republic 51: The New Face of War was erroneously referred to as Star Wars: Republic 51: Protecting Naboo.
